oso.\",\"temperament\": \"Cunning, Cautious, Independent And Affectionate.\",\"weightFemale\": \"22 - 44,1 lb\",\"weightFemaleEs\": \"10 - 20 kg\",\"weightMaleEs\": \"10 - 20 kg\",\"weightMale\": \"22 - 44,1 lb\"},\n" +
